title: Netskope - Network Events
description:
## Netskope - Network Events

This dashboard provides information about the Network events generated by Netskope. Each panel provides a detailed breakdown of the Network events.

definition.content:
# Overview 

- This dashboard provides information about the Network events generated by Netskope. Each panel provides a detailed breakdown of the Network events.

# Widgets
1. Total Events Count
2. User Activity
3. Policy Hits
4. Protocol Hits
5. Network Event Details
6. Network Traffic by Devices
7. Cloud Confidence Level Breakdown
8. Top Sites Visited
9. OS Breakdown along with OS Version
10. Users by Access Methods
11. Bytes Transferred Over Time
12. Packets Transferred Over Time
13. Maximum Session Duration Over Time

definition.title: OS Breakdown along with OS Version
